OBJECTIVES: I.

 Compare the efficacy and safety of two doses of oral valacyclovir in immunocompromised patients with uncomplicated herpes zoster.

 II.

 Compare quality of life, pain, and medical resource utilization in patients treated with these 2 regimens.

